，增幅约45%</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/129cf44ffc0cfe7111a8b4df4cf5ec22/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">中兴通讯</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/cf05ee1f1053c7ebdc9d2fadc0761d56?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">九派Basin流域水文模型上线</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/96c53f9d0e8bf637e6c47fc81f96c034/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">京东健康</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/122f7067b0414de4b6ad9b5a8a75718f?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">卫材新药达卫可 在京东健康首发 为失眠患者提供全新治疗方案</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/488c459718bb9a750996affabf599189/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">蚂蚁集团</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/b6b5051c9952348ee9e8f9b176f3a1d1?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">灵心巧手完成数亿元天使轮融资，蚂蚁集团领投</a><br/><a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/5aade5944bd7df33a9325a915f5ee341?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">蚂蚁数科：自研公链Jovay预计今年9月在主网上线 不涉发币</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/12206edd7570cc5ee81346b046c8467f/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">小米集团</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/c8310fe8f48e5a230fab5f89de291c02?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">小米欧洲市场份额跃居第二，全球稳居前三</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/f45338b67a3c1cb43de264119a481ec8/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">居然之家</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/faac0cb74d0e5864aaa583a075703897?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">上市公司董事长骤然离场！泰康保险七年投资浮亏45.1%</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/c31eac6446f5e417dbf1015143078252/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">爱奇艺</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/b35ee3a3f80423e2c76d7b735f7b9384?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">爱奇艺计划港股二次上市，拟筹资3亿美元</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/e9df0c24dad6f0d175fedf626a3d622f/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">舍得酒业</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/d8b6c78e02d2ed3cbdfbace7dd65de3d?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"